  TO RUN THE  PROGRAM WITH MAKE USE
   make
  to run executable:	./drone
   make clean -will remove the executable and comile file
   (For the second option do not type make clean, it is done in the Script command)	

 SECOND OPTION WITHOUT HAVING TO USE MAKE
	./Scritp
     THE PROGRAM WILL ASK FOR NUMBER OF DRONES
		enter a number and hit ENTER.
	possible error 1 message might occur if there is no file to be removed. That is due to the Script clearing any executable file
	 before runinning.	

 TO INTERRUPT THE EXECUTION OF THE CODE 
      type CONTROL C





		
					
